{"tid":481224,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"資訊科技網站可信度","createTime":"2017-11-27T03:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T04:14:32.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f4dab3ed22fcd0c6761e1cc9ebd1d1cda62d99","tid":481224,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"可信性排名<br />\n1 官方網站<br />\n2 政府網站<br />\n3 學術期刊<br />\n4 大學及教育網站 （Blog除外）<br />\n<br />\n5 維基百科 （人人可編輯。但維基有嚴格的寫作守則，例如不允許原創研究，要quote參考文獻，要有notability。其他人可修正錯誤。所以免費資源中，算係比較可信。因此google也將維基放入high ranking website）<br />\n<br />\n6 討論區 （其他網友可以參與及修正。但通常耐左的post冇人會理。所以比維基差一點）<br />\n<br />\n7 Youtube (開放比人comments的會好些)<br />\n<br />\n8 內容農場 （寫手有錢收，所以好求奇。）<br />\n<br />\n9 Blog (冇人validate，作者一言堂，所以最差 。大機構或名人的blog，又開放比公眾comments的除外)<br />\n<br />\n1-4, 可信資源<br />\n5-7, 中度可信，可以參考<br />\n8-9, 非可信資源，唔睇好過睇"},{"pid":"ba047b5669bc58c5d2f8c62ae4af79e3f42bfe62","tid":481224,"uid":43046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"1 2 6 排最尾呀唔該"},{"pid":"ae7d727b3de0627e68aa7c9422380062d8ca9199","tid":481224,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"REF 知乎網，有關維基百科與百度百科討論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/21315622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F21315622&d=ZyaqgVgDg9HE%2FmGzgwT3t5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3e3f4ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/21315622</a>"}]}